Window Handle
Every page/tab has own id. We need to switch the driver if we want to handle the different windows. 

How can we get the current page id? 
getWindowHandle() --> it will return current page id as String value. 

herokuApp 
New Window 
How we can get all page id on the driver? 
getWindowHandles() --> It will return set of page ids from driver

driver.switch().window(id);

